                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Cadbury Dairy Milk</h3>
                            <p class="mb-2">Status: <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">Halal</span></p>
                            <button class="bg-blue-600 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">Learn More</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-64 bg-blue-950 p-4 text-white flex-shrink-0 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105">
                            <img src="https://jodiabaazar.com/cdn/shop/products/71V9hkFoitL._SL1500.jpg?v=1653597262" alt="Product 10" class="mb-4 h-40 w-full rounded-xl object-cover">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Pringles Original</h3>
                            <p class="mb-2">Status: <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">Halal</span></p>
                            <button class="bg-blue-600 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">Learn More</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-64 bg-blue-950 p-4 text-white flex-shrink-0 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105">
                            <img src="https://hopepharmacy.pk/cdn/shop/products/30_2e5b1e27-6a8e-4faa-b762-91a4690f88d4.jpg?v=1626252940" alt="Product 11" class="mb-4 h-40 w-full rounded-xl object-cover">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Nestle KitKat</h3>
                            <p class="mb-2">Status: <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">Halal</span></p>
                            <button class="bg-blue-600 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">Learn More</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Right Arrow -->
                    <button id="nextButton" class="-translate-y-1/2 right-0 h-10 w-10 bg-gray-800 text-white absolute top-1/2 z-10 flex transform items-center justify-center rounded-full">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <!-- View More Products Button -->
                <div class="mt-6 text-center">
                    <a href="/ProductDisplay" class="bg-blue-950 px-6 py-2 text-white inline-block rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-900">
                        View More Products
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What Our Users Say Section -->
    <section class="mb-10 py-2">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="mb-8 text-blue-950 text-3xl font-semibold">What Our Users Say?</h2>
            <div class="gap-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center">
                <div class="bg-blue-950 p-6 w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/3">
                    <p class="text-white">"I love how easy it is to find halal-certified products! This platform gives me confidence in my choices."</p>
